('004ea22d-4e97-4ebc-9c61-aed1ddfa99ef', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', '0190b6fe-dae2-4875-9b48-ff074e336b5c', 'AC734A08D4A77C1CED7E1D30BEB446BE', '628972285019@s.whatsapp.net', '628972285019@s.whatsapp.net', 'TEXT', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'INCOMING', 'DELIVERED', NULL, '2026-02-09 08:38:21.894', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2026-02-09 08:38:21.895', '2026-02-09 08:38:21.895'),
('012e769b-11a0-43e4-b386-e9f342442da9', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', '0190b6fe-dae2-4875-9b48-ff074e336b5c', NULL, '120363420137806595@g.us', '628972285019:10@s.whatsapp.net', 'TEXT', 'This URL is an **n8n webhook test endpoint**.\n\nHere\'s a breakdown:\n\n1.  **`n8n.meson-digital.com`**: This indicates that the endpoint is hosted on an n8n instance by \"meson-digital.com\". n8n is a powerful open-source workflow automation platform (similar to Zapier or Make.com) that allows you to connect various APIs and services.\n2.  **`/webhook-test/`**: This path explicitly tells you it\'s a \"webhook\" and, more specifically, one set up for \"testing.\"\n3.  **`6ab16e11-ad95-49a9-bd80-3ecdb3fc5851`**: This is a Universally Unique Identifier (UUID). It makes this specific webhook endpoint unique, likely pointing to a particular \"Wait for Webhook\" node within an n8n workflow.\n\n**What happens if you visit it in a browser (GET request):**\n\n*   It is not designed to display a traditional webpage for human interaction.\n*   When you access it via a browser (which sends a GET request), the n8n webhook node will likely register that it received a request.\n*   Often, it will return a simple `200 OK` status, possibly with a plain text message like \"Webhook received,\" \"OK,\" or \"No data received yet,\" to confirm that the endpoint is active and listening.\n*   The actual \"work\" or processing happens when another application sends data (usually via a **POST**, PUT, or DELETE request, often with a JSON body) to this URL. That incoming data would then trigger the associated workflow in n8n.\n\nIn essence, it\'s an address where an n8n workflow is waiting for an external system to send it information to kick off an automated process.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OUTGOING', 'SENT', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2026-02-09 09:27:31.971', '2026-02-09 09:27:31.971'),
