('f224d3aa-068d-4ec1-9ff6-030c30e88c24', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', '0190b6fe-dae2-4875-9b48-ff074e336b5c', NULL, '120363420137806595@g.us', '628972285019:10@s.whatsapp.net', 'TEXT', 'Gg! That stands for \"Good game.\"\n\nIt\'s a common phrase, especially in online gaming, to show sportsmanship at the end of a match, regardless of who won or lost.\n\nHope you had a good game yourself! Is there anything specific you wanted to chat about, or just sharing a friendly \'gg\'?', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OUTGOING', 'SENT', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2026-02-09 09:19:14.305', '2026-02-09 09:19:14.305'),
