('4308d07c-de63-4a12-9fe7-def37a53fe86', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', '2ff85a1e-9aaf-41de-a544-294aaec1185b', 1, NULL, '{\"id\":\"3EB0187673978170F18147\",\"from\":\"120363420137806595@g.us\",\"type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"https://waapitest.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/6ab16e11-ad95-49a9-bd80-3ecdb3fc5851\",\"timestamp\":1770629302}', 200, NULL, '{\"message\":\"This URL points to an **n8n.cloud webhook**.\\n\\nHere\'s what that means:\\n\\n1.  **n8n.cloud:** This is the hosted version of n8n, an open-source workflow automation platform (similar to Zapier or Make/Integromat).\\n2.  **Webhook:** A webhook is a mechanism for one application to provide real-time information to another. Essentially, it\'s a URL that \\\"listens\\\" for incoming data. When data is sent to this URL (usually via an HTTP POST request), it triggers a pre-defined workflow in n8n.\\n\\n**What happens if you click it (or make a GET request to it):**\\n\\n*   **It will trigger an n8n workflow.** When your browser accesses the URL, it sends an HTTP GET request to the webhook.\\n*   **The n8n workflow will receive the request.** Whatever workflow is associated with that specific webhook ID (`6ab16e11-ad95-49a9-bd80-3ecdb3fc5851`) will be activated.\\n*   **Minimal data.** Since it\'s a GET request from a browser, the workflow will receive very little data (no request body, only potential query parameters if you added any).\\n*   **You won\'t see anything useful (likely).** Typically, webhooks are designed to be consumed by other applications, not human browsers. Most n8n webhooks, when triggered by a GET request, will return a generic \\\"OK\\\" message, an empty page, or potentially a custom response if the workflow creator specifically configured one.\\n*   **You cannot see the workflow\'s logic or data.** This URL is merely an entry point. You cannot inspect the internal steps of the n8n workflow or any data it processes/stores by just accessing this URL. That would be a major security flaw.\\n\\n**In summary:** It\'s an endpoint designed to receive automated messages to kick off an automated process. Visiting it directly in a browser isn\'t its intended use and won\'t reveal any sensitive information or the workflow\'s internal workings.\"}', 8878, NULL, '2026-02-09 09:28:29.576'),
('4620013c-89c8-4a15-a0ed-31f5c8b3f4e8', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', '77e88cff-ae4c-4d6f-948f-7a4195c9e295', 1, NULL, '{\"status\":\"CONNECTED\",\"phone_number\":\"628972285019:10\"}', 200, NULL, '', 969, NULL, '2026-02-09 08:43:12.506'),
('4796af6a-d209-418d-8ecc-cc0662143632', 'fa275f1a-f014-479e-9111-97c2f8a67315', 'a763464a-b01c-4061-81ff-471ce1e4223d', 1, NULL, '{\"id\":\"ACD8B27D5196DAF4BBE9F3C542690D37\",\"from\":\"43886412091411@lid\",\"type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"Braga itu bagus ga ya\",\"timestamp\":1770643880}', 200, NULL, '{\"message\":\"CLASSIFICATION: info_singkat\\n\\nBraga sangat bagus jika Anda menyukai suasana kota yang klasik, penuh sejarah, dan ramai!\\n\\n**Kelebihan Braga:**\\n*   **Sejarah & Arsitektur:** Bangunan-bangunan tua bergaya art deco yang indah, cocok untuk penggemar sejarah dan fotografi.\\n*   **Kuliner & Kafe:** Banyak pilihan kafe, restoran, dan bar kekinian maupun legendaris.\\n*   **Hiburan Malam:** Salah satu pusat hiburan malam di Bandung.\\n*   **Fotogenik:** Setiap sudutnya Instagramable, terutama di malam hari dengan lampu-lampu kota.\\n*   **Lokasi Strategis:** Berada di pusat kota, dekat dengan banyak objek wisata lain.\\n\\nBraga sangat cocok untuk wisatawan yang mencari tempat berjalan-jalan santai, menikmati kuliner, atau mencari hiburan.\"}', 3956, NULL, '2026-02-09 13:31:22.254'),
